  abstract: >-
    A position paper on assurance methodology for autonomous AI agents
    deployed by European banks and insurers, articulated as five design
    principles operationalised through a control matrix anchored to the
    AI Act, DORA, ISO/IEC 42001, NIST AI RMF, and OWASP's agent-specific
    threat taxonomy. The repository at the URL above hosts the paper and
    companion artifacts (control matrix, applied case study, reference
